title: STARTER Attends Offshore Energy 2015
text:
STARTER Attends Offshore Energy 2015 Friday, October 23, 2015 by STARTER Show Menu Make An Enquiry 
Offshore Energy 15 is a 23,000mÂ² floor space for a two-day event where 650+ supply chain companies will showcase products and services. 
From all around the world, 15,000 attendees are expected. Starter may not have a booth for this event, but will be there to discuss about the winching solution for your environment. 
As you know, Starter customises solutions for your specific applications in the oil and gas industry. For your mooring, anchoring, lifting, or spooling operations Starter winches and hoists meet ATEX and safety important requirements. 
A Starter offshore expert will be there to help you to define your winching projects.
